{"type":null,"faqId":45783,"title":"手表显示时间无法同步或不准怎么办？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17105153279743671033=\"16\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">手表安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡后，会注册网络，从网络获取时间。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>确认手表<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡未欠费<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>建议用户拨打<span lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span>开通<b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span></b>数据业务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemListText\">注：深圳、上海及部分地区<span lang=\"EN-US\">2G</span>数据业务默认不开通，需要用户拨打<span lang=\"EN-US\">10086</span>开通。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>建议长按手表侧键<span lang=\"EN-US\">10s</span>重启手表，重启后请等待<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>分钟，待手表时间、日期同步<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"ItemStep\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; FONT-SIZE: 7pt; font-stretch: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span>确保周围有<span lang=\"EN-US\">GSM</span>网络，在窗口边、室外等开阔地方尝试。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">注：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">更换<span lang=\"EN-US\">SIM</span>卡也需要长按手表侧键<span lang=\"EN-US\">10s</span>重启手表<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1544","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444265810000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":39,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"k1-g01,荣耀小k,儿童手表,k1,时间,时间不准,时间不对,时间不同步,调整时间,时间同步,时间有误,手表时间,手表日期,如何改时间,时间怎么改,设置时间,时间不准确,时候","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}